Big Picture:

sixtracklib in C/Cl:
  track ( CBlock elems, elemids, nelems,
          CParticles particles,
          nturns,
          CParticles elembyelem
          CParticles turnbyturn)

sixtracklib in python:
  python objects helper class to interact with CBuffers


pysixtrack:
Element:
  validate attributes
  track with the attributes anything Particles-like
  generate CObject
  track using sixtracklib a CParticles

Particles:
  collection of specific coordinates
  generate a CObject








